    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel the <strong>carrots</strong>, quarter them lengthways and cut into batons</p><p>Cut each <strong>beetroot</strong> into 8 wedges</p><p>Place the <strong>carrot</strong> <strong>batons</strong> and <strong>beetroot</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> on a baking tray</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/98_step-2-x200.jpg",
