    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a medium pan over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> and toast for 3 min or until slightly darkened and starting to pop</p><p>Set the toasted pumpkin seeds aside until serving</p>",
